### kodovanie visual
Zapracuj tu 
Gaze-centred representation of an object can be found in both early visual pathway (i.e., retina, lateral geniculate nucleus, striate cortex) and also later in the visual pathway (e.g., extrastriate and parietal cortex). The  epresentations move depending on the gaze because the retinal projection of the project depends on the gaze. To perform a cognitive task as reaching of an object, the brain requires information where an object is located. The location can be determined by information about the object's direction ((horizontal and vertical angular eccentricity)) relative to \textit{fovea} and the distance between the object and eyes. Therefore, earlier visual areas carry out the computation of target direction as seen by a virtual eye between the right and left eye; retinal disparity is calculated as the difference between images from both eyes (Crawford, J. D., et al (2004)).

Takato representacia je pre mozog lacnesia ako head-centered pretoze nevyzaduje integraciu oci ked one 
a autori tvrdia ze sensoricky system tiez koduje auditory and proprioceptive trager in gaze frame
To co je premietane na retine sa potom transmituje do visual cortex v topofraphically arranged maps a eccentricity in theis map definu smer ku objektu s ktorum sa ma neico robit 
vzdialenost je specifikovana retinalnou disparitov a convergence a monocular
Tu ide ako sa to pocita % zapracuj 
v the early movement planning sa tieto signaly rekombinuju do nejdnotnej 3-d representacie priestoru v gaze framev v posterior parietal cortex 

toto ale znamena ze tieto representacie sa musia stae menit ked sa pohnut ocami teda ked sa zmeni gaze aby bola reprezentacia stablibna ... toto sa nazyva updating alebo remapping 
updatuje sa tiez pre rotaciu a pre translationa pocas head a body movements
opis obrazku mozno dobre tam dat obrazok a 
ukazalo sa ze toto moze mozog robit aj ked dame pred vision, len pouzitim signalov z oculomotor system ohladom pohybu oci
vyzara to tak ze hat the areas in and around the medial bank of the intraparietal sulcus of the parietal cortex play a major role in representing and remapping reach targets in gaze-centered coordinates.
Receptivne fieldy of individual parieral neurons sa hybu ked ked pohyb oci corresponduje ku remmapovanie of the target 
Remappovanie bolo preukazane v n the posterior parietal cortex through human functional magnetic resonance imaging studies. ecent neural recordings in the monkey show evidence of updating in a number of extrastriate visual areas such as areas V3A, V3, and V2.
Sa zda ze tieto oblasti by mohli hraju rolu pri remappovani pre reach movments. 

#Motor Coding of Reach Movements
Mozog musi navrhnut pohyb v refernce frame relative to shoulder. 
PRe specifikovanie 3-d reach plan pobrebuje byt znama aplituda nahrhovaneho pohubu a smer. Viacero studii indikuje ze sme a ampltude mozu byt kodovane nezavisle, na druhej strane europhysiological recordings of neural activity in the dorsal premotor cortex pocas planvovanie reach ukazali ze amplituda a smer su kodovane spolu v jednom neruone. Mozu to byt viacere riesenia ako to rozmotat ze na urovni neuronu je to kodovane spolu  ale su citane rozlicnymi mechanizmami na generovanie aktivacii svalov.
Kodovanie movement vector v explicitnej representacii shoulder-centere boli najdene u ocicej vectral premotor cortex, mensie porcie neuronov in dorsal premotor cortex a v the primary motor cortex tiez ukazali toto 
Taka reprezetacie coexist s inou, viac muscle-related  represetation, ktora mozu reflektovat transformaciu tychto codov do aktivacie svalou

takze motor plan v shc rd musiac byt prelozene do aktivacii svalov na pohyb, kde sa musi brat do uvahy nielen smer ale aj akou sily pre kazdy sval
do uvahy sa mus vrat pozicia sucastna ruky
ale kedze je vizualny input v GCRF tak sa mus urobit transfoacia do motor command pre ruku v SHCRF. 
#Visualmotor transforamtion
Nato aby sa mohlo vypocitat movement vector musi sa brat do uvahy rozdiel medzi rukov teraz a poziciou ruky, nato aby sa to dalo porovnat tak musime mat v oblasti ktora vykonava tento vypocet informacie o ruka aj targete a ich reprezentaciu musia byt v rovnakom RF, nevie sa ktora to robi area a v ktorom RF
Toto porovananie ruky a ciela moze vyuzivat ciacere reprezentacie v roznych casti mozgy a je tiez zname ze mozog moze ziskavat informacie z roznych zdrojoch a v zmysle senzorickej integracie combinat ich tak aby dostal najvieryhodnejsie pozorovanie.
Toto by znamenalo ze pristup ku rovnakej informacii ale v rozlicnych RF a podla toho aka je uloha. 
Ale aj tak je potrebna transformacie z GC do SH, ci uz je to robene nezavisle pre hand a taget alebo combinovane ako desired movent vector. 

Berie sa do uvahy aj rotacei a translacie celeho tela lebo napriklad oko sa pohne v priestore ked sa pohne hlava, teda casti mozgu cor transformaciu musia mat infoamcie o rotacii a oci a halvy tak aby bola ok reprezentacie hand and targer.

\end{comment}


